{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "504d50ba-9bff-4512-bf16-96062feca312", "type": 201, "content": {"answer_steps": [], "preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/504d50ba-9bff-4512-bf16-96062feca312@1.pkg/1772597708423/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597709368", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/504d50ba-9bff-4512-bf16-96062feca312@1.pkg/1772597708423/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597709368"}, "identifier": "504d50ba-9bff-4512-bf16-96062feca312", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">本题考查保持心理健康。</span></p><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">A：活动主题聚焦心理健康，旨在帮助青少年形成积极心态，增强心理韧性，故A符合题意；</span></p><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">B：&ldquo;消除青春烦恼，心理冲突&rdquo;表述绝对化，心理冲突是成长中的正常现象，活动可缓解但无法完全消除，故B说法错误；</span></p><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">C：&ldquo;杜绝心理问题&rdquo;表述错误，心理问题无法完全杜绝，活动只能预防和减少，故C说法错误；</span></p><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">D：活动主题为心理健康，与&ldquo;生理知识&rdquo;&ldquo;道德修养&rdquo;无直接关联，故D不符合题意；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">故本题选A。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）近日，